<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Page Not Found</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #e74c3c;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555;
    }
    a {
      color: #3498db;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
    <p>The URL <strong>${req.url}</strong> was not found on this server.</p>
    <p><a href="/">Go back to homepage</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>